{"tid":1321533,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(裝備撚）移 動 式 連 儂 牆","createTime":"2019-07-15T16:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T20:35:21.000Z","uid":15394,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d01ef696b57a086294cb57389ff5cf6f3b5bd157","tid":1321533,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:43:06.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n發夢去左幾次遊行，<br />\n<br />\n撞到個廢老笑鳩班示威者標語又唔舉下，<br />\n係到鳩叫鳩行，<br />\nD on9連儂牆整完又搬唔到，<br />\n<br />\n比人打又冇野擋，<br />\n要自衛又得把死人遮，<br />\n<br />\n我問佢「咁你有乜高見呀廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />」<br />\n佢同我講：<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「和理非 + 勇武 = 移動式連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！！！！！！」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n之後就比左呢個秘笈我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話帶出街去遊行，<br />\n高舉標語係天經地義！！！！<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n所需物資<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>1. 浮版（decathlon $64) / 紙皮（$0）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KgV1DUV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKgV1DUV.png&h=535d9e4e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">2. Memo紙 （$0，公司拎）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pao27Oz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPao27Oz.png&h=4019adeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>3. 衣物伸縮棍/枴杖 (Aeon $12) /鴨記或迪卡儂行山杖（$67） / 藤條 ($0，發發聲，打仔必備）<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CDEqk8T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCDEqk8T.png&h=9221b873&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TriZqAz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTriZqAz.png&h=0e34960c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQsLk8U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQsLk8U.png&h=c6c33f5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">4. 索帶</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n自己諗方法索埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n示意圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mCvxf0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mCvxf0.png&h=496530ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/48Zt3nG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F48Zt3nG.png&h=6ba972ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n記住遊行要有標語，<br />\n印唔切記就自己痴memo整連儂牆！！！！<br />\n咁大家先知遊行訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"824493d03a12a55239e922022f800b635c07044b","tid":1321533,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:44:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7b5d1ea43e2e25e53b4cd79ce92e2e2a33a5f61c","tid":1321533,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:44:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"07dcf17b7758a4a33b7006815bc2e05bb53fffd8","tid":1321533,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"預計五毛今晚又準備轉風向<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1c73d3b57520028d79716673be2a12144308864","tid":1321533,"uid":15394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:46:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"5e6e240c83f06efa782f4060bd24be5aea572282","tid":1321533,"uid":18171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T16:46:31.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6dd324d69b507016e33b